## 7. アイコン実装の詳細

### Lucideアイコンライブラリの使用

**CDN読み込み:**
```html
<script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
```

**使用方法:**
```html
<i data-lucide="droplets" class="lucide-icon"></i>

<script>
  lucide.createIcons();
</script>
```

### または、SVGで直接実装

各アイコンのSVGコード（簡略版）を直接記述することも可能です。

**droplets:**
```html
<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M7 16.3c2.2 0 4-1.83 4-4.05 0-1.16-.57-2.26-1.71-3.19S7.29 6.75 7 5.3c-.29 1.45-1.14 2.84-2.29 3.76S3 11.1 3 12.25c0 2.22 1.8 4.05 4 4.05z" fill="#5A8F7B"/>
  <path d="M12.56 6.6A10.97 10.97 0 0 0 14 3.02c.5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5s3 3.5 3 5.5a6.98 6.98 0 0 1-11.91 4.97" stroke="#5A8F7B" stroke-width="2"/>
</svg>
```

**dog:**
```html
<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <circle cx="8" cy="16" r="1" fill="#5A8F7B"/>
  <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="1" fill="#5A8F7B"/>
  <path d="M10 16v6M14 16v6M8 10l-2-2M16 10l2-2" stroke="#5A8F7B" stroke-width="2"/>
</svg>
```

**plus:**
```html
<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19" stroke="#5A8F7B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" stroke="#5A8F7B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
</svg>
```

**store:**
```html
<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <rect x="4" y="10" width="16" height="10" stroke="#5A8F7B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
  <path d="M4 10L12 4L20 10" stroke="#5A8F7B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
</svg>
```

